{"tid":1555290,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"過左9.8，我地係時候部署下一步","createTime":"2019-09-09T10:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T10:33:39.000Z","uid":231007,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ecdd5170a60553a3ac8fc8e75ed827ad2d7a16dd","tid":1555290,"uid":231007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:04:02.000Z","msg":"星期日的遊行好成功 <br />\n但悲痛既係每一日都有手足被捕，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">甚至被自殺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以只依靠美國國會緩助我地<br />\n我地都要諗定下一步點做<br />\n如果國會唔過咁點呢？<br />\n過左下一步又點做？<br />\n<br />\n三個月的革命令真正的香港人開始團結勇敢對抗不公<br />\n呢場運動我地一定要步步為營！<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！<br />\n我愛香港！"},{"pid":"14dafb4693eb7720dfbaf09509300e8b0575953c","tid":1555290,"uid":94494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:07:44.000Z","msg":"一帶一路峰會將在9月11-12日 在香港會展中心舉行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1495234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1495234</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"09e5fd1a44b382b1688df117095627882d9b652c","tid":1555290,"uid":2645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"915 儲氣 士氣唔好跌"},{"pid":"430c263562103b6cd38fdc37205e842a84ad7de2","tid":1555290,"uid":226413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:10:13.000Z","msg":"儲左好耐氣<br />\n唔係要部署下一步<br />\n係要認清下一步、承認下一步"},{"pid":"5f454e8b0acd04f37b58083b470c51b1bd9218d1","tid":1555290,"uid":226413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"430c263562103b6cd38fdc37205e842a84ad7de2","tid":1555290,"uid":226413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:10:13.000Z","msg":"儲左好耐氣<br />\n唔係要部署下一步<br />\n係要認清下一步、承認下一步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:10:34.000Z","msg":"其實大家都應該知道下一步係咩"},{"pid":"5cb2cbdb7d68f4f9279f58a29fa3e48253ed0976","tid":1555290,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\